{"tid":1200604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夜晚唔好衝，真係唔好，留12號朝早","createTime":"2019-06-10T19:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:14:08.000Z","uid":118228,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"697beb77c8fed06c310ddcc89fe3f49cc98e1ada","tid":1200604,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:16:08.000Z","msg":"岩岩個次最後留低個d好多好後生無乜經驗，走都唔識走。求下大家見唔夠人真係唔好亂咁黎，唔夠人都無法，留番精力朝早夠人慢慢黎。<br />\n<br />\n我幾年前已經試過好多次呢種感覺，好嬲好唔甘心，點都想留到最後個下，所以我明，堅明，不過都係要留住條命先，聽晚佢地見有人一定打到冚家鏟，點都等到開會先。Please"},{"pid":"318e6ed97fa0be5561b3363e27d913625b7e63ee","tid":1200604,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e972bd033007cbd3a7baf52c97d527f488321453","tid":1200604,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55950309824e3a45ab51d6f1545b64f4a9fd8eaa","tid":1200604,"uid":97840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d4f020cff3c6e316ff27eea6c2d08dcc3f100a7","tid":1200604,"uid":136415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3219c5eb860a77597c7d1064a5e2ff68068fca3","tid":1200604,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:30:27.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n夜晚冇車走"},{"pid":"efb7baa658c594642542f523f0d115f60bbd6018","tid":1200604,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"自推 拜託留力"}]}